{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_71","type":"agent_message","text":"The `spring.factories` path is still dead under native image even with a merged resource, which means continuing to model Boot 2.5’s factory discovery purely through resources is likely wasted effort here. I’m pivoting the TCK app classes to explicit auto-configuration imports so the test exercises the same starter configuration without depending on `SpringFactoriesLoader` discovery at native runtime."}}
